{"tid":2100054,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] PES MOBILE 2020 討論帖(238) AC88 國米88","createTime":"2020-07-08T18:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T18:58:45.000Z","uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6b32e419cea52dd5ced76175ca976b41e1f36c","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPToUF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPToUF5.jpg&h=ebe22e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ra2szs4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fra2szs4.jpg&h=3bcaeb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n● 官網：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.konami.com%2Fwepes%2Fmobile%2Fen%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=c1105cc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/</a><br />\n● Download Link<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fpes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer%2Fid1117270703%3Fmt%3D8&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=1b3489c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.konami.pesam&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=59169c8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam</a><br />\n<br />\n● 新手開波Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗唔洗刷首抽?<br />\n新手開波既時候會有好多抽，盡量黑波起手，coins留黎抽Fp(精選球員)，唔滿意既可以繼續刷到自己想要既球員為止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣改Email或者密碼?<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.konami.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.konami.net%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=d2b47539\" target=\"_blank\">https://my.konami.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 操控方法<br />\n操控類型有 Advanced 同 Classic 揀<br />\n推薦 Classic 佢類似手制咁樣同埋易上手啲<br />\n<br />\n● 球員資料<br />\nPES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=c326b0ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n要注意由於可能有球員更新，所以DATABASE 入面既100%抽球員可能有誤。<br />\n<br />\n只需要直接search球員名，你就可以搵到該球員特性同數值。<br />\n而想搵一堆某類球員，可以憑Search Conditions自行set Filters 搵出黎。<br />\n<br />\n● 不同底色球員資料<br />\n<span class=\"red\">紅色</span>=強化版legend(非常難中)(使用該球會球衣有加乘)（<span class=\"red\">球員會保留至下季</span>）<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">金色</span>=普通版legend<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\">紫色</span>=強化版現役(現實比賽中表現良好的球員會出現係fp pool到)或club selection <br />\n<span class=\"blue\">藍色</span>=普通版現役，跟隨現實球員表現，狀態會不同(可以3個黑波換一個)<br />\n灰色=舊版現役，狀態永遠C(2019版本或之前)<br />\n<br />\n●畫面調整<br />\n新手入game 第一件事畫質轉60fps<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h38hp4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh38hp4m.jpg&h=66c1328d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但30fps low quality 比較慳電<br />\n<br />\n教練，球員，沒有最強只有更強<br />\n因該每次更新，Konami 都會暗改教練球員走位，唔會通知，要靠老手用過先知<br />\n<br />\n●實時系統<br />\n每周四維護6小時（10am-4pm)後，會按照現實球員表現而調整球員狀態；<br />\n另有巴打 隨時更新球員實際操作表現（暗改），詳情要留意留言<br />\n<br />\n●教練更新<br />\n即日起，可簽入不同版本的同名教練。每日更新3次，已擁有的教練不能再簽下<br />\n<br />\n●拍賣<br />\n根本球員條件（國籍，球會，年歲，能力）買球探組合球員<br />\n詳情：PES DATABASE<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=c326b0ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n<br />\n●賺取Gp方法<br />\n<br />\nOpen challenge ，打哂三關有75000gp<br />\n<br />\nMatchday ，除左部分比賽有coins外，每關夠1500積分，可以觀戰賺取gp<br />\n<br />\n季節賽掛tour(適宜新手)，以白銅銀波掛機，升班可以賺取23000~24000gp<br />\n<br />\n●遊戲玩法<br />\n<br />\nTour &amp;Tour Sim<br />\n用fp球員既%會高d (分數較高)<br />\n<br />\n最少打2500 points 賺導師(幫球員升lv)<br />\n<br />\ncampaign sim <br />\n<br />\n刷gp 用狀態A/B 銀波+白波bench(升班有23000gp~24000gp)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n●Matchday<br />\n<br />\n有coins既matchday 就打夠5500分<br />\n想刷gp可以繼續打 前300名可以參加比賽(抽籤)<br />\n無coins既matchday 打1500分就得 記得觀戰賺gp<br />\n<br />\n兩種玩法<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\">Preset  team</span><br />\n使用該球會的藍底球員，不扣合約費<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nio69mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNio69mb.jpg&h=67e7dcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9BCjKUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9BCjKUD.jpg&h=8b21b409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\">自已球員代表球會出戰</span><br />\n自由選擇代表一個球會，使用該球會球員球隊值會更高，獲得更多積分，且狀態必定A<br />\n<br />\n球隊值：<br />\nlegend 或Fp 800％<br />\n藍底 480％<br />\n灰底 400％<br />\n敵對球員 50％<br />\n<br />\n例子（選擇國際米蘭）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HMNORUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHMNORUZ.jpg&h=00df984f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Grhy21P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrhy21P.jpg&h=003923f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下星期打傳奇活動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0F7KChz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0F7KChz.jpg&h=d97eed7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNTBtpp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNTBtpp.jpg&h=bad9b5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷年連登杯冠軍名單<br />\n<br />\n2020UEFA:                     月城雪兔<br />\n2020World cup:              出奧燒啦<br />\n2020歐洲x南美杯:          出奧燒啦<br />\n2500戰力杯:                    Aristo<br />\n第二屆普黑團體盃賽:      Aristo 一生人三次 waiiiiiiii 我朋友係金毛獅王<br />\nLegend盃：                    出奧燒啦、AC米蘭、 鳩改住先、球皇balotelli<br />\n                                      <br />\nPes mobile三巨頭<br />\n牛<br />\n兔<br />\n啤"},{"pid":"16247473bda3d146c92d1ddf69018c65d81e409e","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:08.000Z","msg":"Go?"},{"pid":"22709c7dfb9cb6001913aab90283933d38450583","tid":2100054,"uid":203961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"金毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7762a3ec4a7e5e3b8d9ef2d9c048dc62f9ede38","tid":2100054,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16247473bda3d146c92d1ddf69018c65d81e409e","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:08.000Z","msg":"Go?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"go"},{"pid":"51eee36ebf4959683d8d6d2409136ce71a7cc6c8","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7762a3ec4a7e5e3b8d9ef2d9c048dc62f9ede38","tid":2100054,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16247473bda3d146c92d1ddf69018c65d81e409e","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:08.000Z","msg":"Go?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"go"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:03:27.000Z","msg":"有人排緊隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未熟新陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c129ec3d86a7a7d412d7e7ac4bab3b2fc4edfbc6","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"紗夏さん?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb6bb322d85110183f11edf092335126a8e644a","tid":2100054,"uid":251708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7762a3ec4a7e5e3b8d9ef2d9c048dc62f9ede38","tid"